Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:59.10,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}優しく食むわ　あなたの全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:04.30,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:17.65,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}仄青い混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:22.61,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冷たく私を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.07,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:27.59,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}そして抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:34.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}あなたのいないその体で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.93,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}吐き出しその生命は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:44.28,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}まだ形を残しているわ　紅く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}鮮やかな永遠が見えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:50.98,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}隣でそれは歌いだすわ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.10,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}What was I born for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:57.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}ねえ　私を愛して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:02.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}離さないから
